entries.arrived_at_loc: Wait here for the transport, pilot.
entries.complete: Success! The transport has reached its destination.
entries.failed_destroy: The transport was destroyed. Mission failed.
entries.failed_protect: Mission failed! The transport was lost...
entries.goodbye_3: The Force be with you, friend!
entries.hull_half: Whoa! Our hull is at fifty percent!
entries.quest_escort_d: Fly along-side the Alliance transport as it makes its way to the Rebel Outpost. Destroy any hostile fighters that you come across.
entries.quest_location_d: The Alliance is moving its cargo through the Kashyyyk system and plans to stop off at the Rebel Outpost.
entries.quest_rendezvous_d: You will find the Alliance transport at this location. Fly there and escort the ship to its final destination.
entries.reason_1: Help us get to the Rebel outpost!
entries.reason_2: We need to get this shipment to the Rebel Outpost.
entries.reason_3: Got a load of ceremonial decorations for the Rebel outpost!
entries.reason_4: I need to get this cargo to the Rebel outpost as soon as possible!
entries.reason_5: We're in route to the Rebel outpost!
entries.taunt_3: The Grhag will have their revenge!
entries.taunt_4: You are no match for the Ghrag!
entries.title: Escort an Alliance Transport to the Rebel Outpost in Kashyyyk
entries.title_d: An Alliance transport carrying ceremonial statues, hologram awards, and various personal items is on its way to the Rebel outpost in Kashyyyk. Ensure it makes it there safely and you will be handsomely rewarded.
